<h3>Animation</h3>
<p><strong>Sequential</strong> animation displays sea ice for every month, and <strong>monthly</strong> animation cycles through sea ice data for the same month over different years.</p>
<div class="btn-group" data-toggle="buttons-radio">
	<button class="btn" id="mapAnimationSequential">Sequential</button>
	<button class="btn" id="mapAnimationMonthly">Monthly</button>
</div>
<div class="btn-group">
	<button class="btn" id="mapAnimationPlay"><i class="icon-play"></i></button>
	<button class="btn" id="mapAnimationPause"><i class="icon-pause"></i></button>
</div>
